The [[Aratech Repulsor Company/Legends|Aratech]] '''sound dampening belt''', or '''SD belt''' for short, was a [[sound dampening stealth unit]] manufactured by the Aratech Repulsor Company in the period following the [[Jedi Civil War]]. It reduced all sound that the user emitted, and even helped to protect against [[Sonic weapon/Legends|sonic weapons]].

